&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.bigledger.com/applets/tenant-admin-applet/" &gt;Tenant Admin Applet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - System administration and configuration&lt;/li&gt;
